+# Architecture
+
+## Design Principles
+
+1. **Skill Isolation**: Each skill does one job well
+2. **Composability**: Skills can be reordered or replaced
+3. **Knowledge-Driven**: Security patterns and rubrics are versioned in git
+4. **Dual Analysis**: Heuristics (fast, offline) + LLM (contextual, deep)
+
+## Pipeline Flow
+
+```
+User Input (PR diff)
+  ↓
+[ingest-pr] → Parse and normalize
+  ↓
+[summarize-diff] → High-level summary
+  ↓
+[security-pass] → Security scan (OWASP, CWE)
+  ↓
+[tests-and-risk] → Test coverage analysis
+  ↓
+[compose-review] → Final verdict + recommendations
+  ↓
+Output (Markdown + JSON)
+```
+
+## Tools
+
+- **read-diff-context**: Parses unified diffs
+- **write-review-artifact**: Writes final review files
+
+## Knowledge Base
+
+- `security-patterns.md`: OWASP Top 10, CWE mappings, framework checks
+- `review-rubric.md`: Blocking vs non-blocking criteria
+
+## Extensibility
+
+To add custom rules:
+1. Update `knowledge/security-patterns.md` with new patterns
+2. Add corresponding checks to `scripts/local-heuristics.mjs` (optional)
+3. Skills will automatically incorporate new knowledge
